Table of Contents

Name

pacparser_setmyip - Sets my IP address.

Synopsis

#include <pacparser.h>

void pacparser_setmyip(const char *ip);

Parameters

const char *ip
Custom IP address.

Description

Sets my IP address to a custom value. This is the IP address returned by myIpAddress() javascript function.
